PCR Name: Remove Micron 2550 SSD from CS24 Sync prejects
Change Request: Ø 1.  PCR request This PCR is to request removal of Micron 2550 SSD from CS24 Sync prejects.  Ø 2.  Background Micron 2550 SSD has MP gating issue caused hung up during OOBE Data retention test. 2550 SSD does not qualify to Lenovo's requirements. Micron's investigation for the root cause and FW solution is taking very long time, finally Micron internally decided to cancel 2550 product due to 2650 will be ready in 24Q4. Since Micron internally cancelled 2550, Lenovo Storage Dev. decided to remove Micron 2550 from the Sync prejects sourcing list. Ø 3.  Required actions: Remove Micron 2550 SSD from Sync prejects of CS24 system.  Remove Micron 2550 SSD from the sourcing plan. Ø 4.  Drive information to be removed from Source Plan SSS1D71499---Micron 2550 256GB 2280 SSS1D71500---Micron 2550 512GB 2280 SSS1D71501---Micron 2550 1TB 2280

PCR Name: Alkaline Batteries removed request - DT
Change Request: Background: Received GEO info that Columbia ban Alkaline Batteries import, which would impact some of our wireless Keyboard and mouse, checking with Accessory BU and our BB owner, we find that some more countries also have similar requirement for years, the impact countries as below: - Mexico, LA - Brazil, LA - Argentine, LA - Colombia, LA - Paraguay, LA - Ecuador, LA - South Korea, AP - Malaysia, AP We could only find the evidence for Colombia, Argentina & Brazil. And we also have the original mail which including the whole country list. (Columbia Informa cion_importante-para-importadores-de-pilas-al-momento-de-la-importacion.pdf) (Argentina Resolucion N 970.pdf) (CONAMA 401 battery law (Brazil law).pdf) (Alkaline Batteries.msg) Need evaluate the solution to remove the Alkaline Batteries in box ASAP. And we also need double check whether the Alkaline battery info or image been show on the box or any special UG.

share PCB w/ M90q G5

IC Tower08IRH & YTM400IRH & QTM660C share one BIOS; 5. IC Tower08IRH enable ROW.

PCR Name: Change Neo Ultra BTB bracket to Line Fit part
Change Request: Background: Neo Ultra have two kinds of BTB BKT because of dual fan thermal impact. No fool proof design for BTB BKT, there will be high quality and rework risk if asking LNV MFG to replace this BKT. Proposal:  Propose to change two kinds of BTB BKT to line fit part to reduce quality risk and avoid scrapping part.   For HEC YOGA Portal, only have 65W config, no need to change. (Sample.png)

PCR Name: LAS NYCE Logo to be Remove from Labels in all Products
Change Request: LAS is in a transition process of certification organism in MEXICO due to a saving in costs and they will no longer work with ISATEL as after a benchmark Lenovo local office found better cost/benefit working with another Certificate Organism named ANCE. ISATEL is a Laboratory which used to work with NYCE, ANCE is a laboratory and a Certificate Organism. In the transition process ISATEL is improving their costs by changing to GCS Organism and thy are now facing a dilemma with current projects. They are requesting support to aligning with each BU the following change for all product segments: Remove NYCE Logo from Regulatory Label(D Cover) and Box Label. Keep NOM Logo as is the only one mandatory logo for the regulation (See the below reference). This may be a challenging adjustment, but they have consulted the implies this may have, and can do this transition the whole 2024 year. They are telling our contacts to start these new adjustments for all new Projects rather than change it for current ones. There is no implication on removing NYCE Logo, but as we are now working with NYCE’s competitors ANCE & GCS there might be penalties in the future if they continue using NYCE logo. If a current project includes NYCE logo and the NOM Certificate was issued by GCS or ANCE we still have a grace period to continue using it, but all projects in 2025 must remove NYCE logo.(NOM-016-SCFI-2017.pdf)

Introduce Lenovo Close Loop Recycling PCC into KBDMS
Change Request: To follow company ESG strategy and enhance corporate responsibility, we would like to introduce a new process/certification called " Lenovo Close Loop Recycling" into DT KBDMS. Target: Use recycled Lenovo ABS to build Lenovo KBD/MS, first go with 20% close loop without cost up. (95% PCC including 20% Lenovo close loop material + 70% industry ITE material) 1st wave SS scope: Calliope USB KDB/MS & Traditional USB KBD; 2nd wave: other wireless KBD. Launch schedule: 1st wave at End of 2024. (Calliope USB follow new Gen.3 schedule), promoted at 2025 CES roadshow as ESG. - HP is teeying to leverag our working progress and target to inroduce their close loop recycle product at middle of 2025. Detial: Build up new process & certification standard with UL. (Liu Yang) PCC Vendors need processed UL certification, Lenovo will also add close loop certification when apply new KBD/MS. Target: No cost impact, no feature impact, so can do running change when available.

PCR Name: Unify on-board M.2 SSD screws for RPL_R Intel PCB2&PCB3 MB
Change Request: Background: QT M550 On-board M.2 SSD falls off after ELP reliability shock test.The final solution was to change the M.2 SSD screw spec to a large size. Since Intel PCB 2& PCB 3 also use the on-board M.2 SSD design and have the same risks. We recommend to uniform the M.2 SSD screw size to avoid the problems.  Solution: Remove 1pcs M.2 SSD old screw SM20H54735 from BOM.And add 1pcs Candyman screw for on-board M.2 SSD. (After.png) (Before.png) (Screw.png)

We recommend to uniform the M.2 SSD screw size to avoid the problems.  Solution: Remove 1pcs M.2 SSD old screw SM20H54735 from BOM.And add 1pcs Candyman screw for on-board M.2 SSD. (After.png) (Before.png) (Screw.png)

PCR Name: ANZ ban foamed plastics in packaging - DT
Change Request: Background: Western Australia will ban foamed plastics from July 1st, 2025, the ACT is focus on EPS (expanded polystyrene) but mentioned “other foamed plastics” also in scope, means our cushion material as EPE are impacted based on current info. We need find the solution to meet Western Australia’s regulation.   Schedule: July 1st, 2025, customer clearance data for Australia   Scope: All products SS to Western Australia, only those products weighting over 45kg are exempt.   Evidence reference: (WA stage-2-ban-plan-for-plastics-eps-moulded-pack.pdf)

We need find the solution to meet Western Australia’s regulation.   Schedule: July 1st, 2025, customer clearance data for Australia   Scope: All products SS to Western Australia, only those products weighting over 45kg are exempt.   Evidence reference: (WA stage-2-ban-plan-for-plastics-eps-moulded-pack.pdf)

PCR Name: neoP900cIRR add cardreader back.
Change Request: Background:  - neoP900cIRR drop cardreader but after checking SIT sample, front bezel still remian. - As neoP900cIRR MB share with YTM460 can support card reader but only need to qualify it. - SMB geo agree to enable card reader. but need to remove card reader from front bezel with neoP900cIRR 17L flex chassis release.   Action: - Pull in neoP900cIRR SS from 3.29 -> 3.15 w/o card reader; - Card reader will be enable in 3.29; - Remove card reader from front bezel with neoP900cIRR 17L flex chassis release.

PCR Name: Traditional USB KB new gen w/ AI Key design demand
Change Request: Due to MSFT require AI Key on KB on all PC w/ Win before July/2025, and avoid run in change on REL product, we need traditional USB KBMS to be updated to new version w/ AI Key.   AI Key design guidance: AI key immediately to the right of right Alt key. Windows menu key and right Ctrl key are to the right of this. Involved product: TC M90a gen5,TC M90a pro gen4

PCR Name: A970 135W电源+非充电底座搭配开放
Change Request: 目前有一客户标书有要求135W以上电源，项目总计8K+ 单一配置，搭配135W需求约3k左右。通常不同标书有不同需求，中国区希望电源未来也是大的cover小的scope，方便前端灵活选择。经预评估，认证及测试均无额外投入，可直接开放。

PCR Name: Add MRP label PN in BOM for India onshore order on Commercial and SMB India model
Change Request: At present: MFG use SO number=422 to print India MRP label,for offshore order, no MRP label required.  there will be a risk to miss the label printing in this way.  Consumer DT already add this PN in BOM to recognize India onshore order, we propose to leverage this rule to Think products too. Mfg plants will print MRP label based on dummy PN in BOM, we will not recognize SO type anymore.BOM rule should be: India onshore order, will have PN SPP0M57073 in BOM, India offshore order will not have this PN in BOM. The method of Consumer DT is CV in special char. for creating India  Onshore/Offshore MTMs PN used in Consumer products: SBB0K60798       SPP0M57073       Dummy PN for MRP PKG LBL print (Sample of India MRP Label.png)

PCR Name: 中国区QT富士康机型独立网卡引入需求
Change Request: Dears, 随着市场的变化，富士康机型启天M450C/M540C已经开放全行业接单，并非之前M4C聚焦新兴市场。现在市场上价格竞争特别激烈，而启天成本最优的产品为M4C系列，因此很多制造业企业、教育客户等需要双网卡需求的项目，M450承接的成本压力太大，需要M4C系列+独立网卡进行应对，需求评估富士康机型全线引入独立网卡的周期及NRE费用。希望可以SS时间为5月份。 量级方面，目前正在招标的项目年采购量8k，联想份额40%左右（今年目标拿下更大占比），教育项目预计在下季度陆续放量，7-9月份是教育大的采购季节，需要提前做好产品技术储备。 Scope：启天M450C\M460C\M660C SS tgt：最佳时间4月份，可接受时间5月份（需同客户沟通推迟交付） Biz case：~30k/y 附件为本次招标的相关信息，供参考。（请勿外传！！）(QT.png)

PCR Name: 商用中国区出厂预装KB以满足GB18030规定

PCR Name: TCO 10 implement
Change Request: Background: Most of WW ThinkCentre M, ThinCentre neo(TDT) and some special consumer(mini) model need TCO certified. TCO released the TCO 10 draft 2 version, since there are lots impaction based on this version, and the time is very limited until the TCO 10 final launch, so submit the PCR and just based on draft 2 standard. (tco-certified-generation-10-for-desktops-draft-2.pdf) (tco-certified-generation-10-for-all-in-one-pcs-draft-2.pdf) TCO 10 Schedule: Feb.2024: TCO 10 Draft 2（Feb 20 – Mar 20, open for comments） Jun.2024: TCO 10 (Final criteria) Dec.2024: TCO 10 Certificate launch and TCO 9 disabled for new application Nov.2026: TCO 9 Certificate EOL   Key update need action(until draft 2): 1. Products must be marked with a unique identifier(reference “guide-for-unique-product-identifier-criteria-draft-2.pdf”), need a QR Code and a UPI URL for each product (guide-for-unique-product-identifier-criteria-draft-2.pdf) 2. Recycled packaging materials: Required 50%+ PCC material usage for plastic packaging parts, we could not meet now. Need decide new solution ASAP. 3. Flame retardant & stabilizer usage: All housing ME plastic part(including socket or inlet)>0.5g, PCB(those PCB sealed inside of the component are exempted), external cable could only use the FR or S substance listed in TCO accepted substance list(ASL): TCO Certified Accepted Substance List — safer alternatives to hazardous 4. Plasticizer usage: All housing ME plastic part(including socket or inlet)>0.5g, cable & wire(those cable/wire sealed inside of the component are exempted) could only use the PL substance listed in TCO accepted substance list(ASL): TCO Certified Accepted Substance List — safer alternatives to hazardous 5. Extended warranty periods: Brand owners must offer a product warranty for five years of which at least one year is free of charge. The price for the warranty after the free period must not exceed 15% of the product price, per year. 6. Improved availability of software updates: Free security and functionality software updates for the operating system must be available throughout the validity period of the TCO Certified certificate and at least five years after the product is no longer placed on the market. 7. Display panel factories: require the panel factories comply with the similar criteria as final assessment factories, such as ISO cert and safer process chemical usage etc. 8. Some other update related to facotry green energy usage, corporate level e-waste management etc.

(tco-certified-generation-10-for-desktops-draft-2.pdf) (tco-certified-generation-10-for-all-in-one-pcs-draft-2.pdf) TCO 10 Schedule: Feb.2024: TCO 10 Draft 2（Feb 20 – Mar 20, open for comments） Jun.2024: TCO 10 (Final criteria) Dec.2024: TCO 10 Certificate launch and TCO 9 disabled for new application Nov.2026: TCO 9 Certificate EOL   Key update need action(until draft 2): 1. Products must be marked with a unique identifier(reference “guide-for-unique-product-identifier-criteria-draft-2.pdf”), need a QR Code and a UPI URL for each product (guide-for-unique-product-identifier-criteria-draft-2.pdf) 2. Recycled packaging materials: Required 50%+ PCC material usage for plastic packaging parts, we could not meet now. Need decide new solution ASAP. 3. Flame retardant & stabilizer usage: All housing ME plastic part(including socket or inlet)>0.5g, PCB(those PCB sealed inside of the component are exempted), external cable could only use the FR or S substance listed in TCO accepted substance list(ASL): TCO Certified Accepted Substance List — safer alternatives to hazardous 4. Plasticizer usage: All housing ME plastic part(including socket or inlet)>0.5g, cable & wire(those cable/wire sealed inside of the component are exempted) could only use the PL substance listed in TCO accepted substance list(ASL): TCO Certified Accepted Substance List — safer alternatives to hazardous 5. Extended warranty periods: Brand owners must offer a product warranty for five years of which at least one year is free of charge. The price for the warranty after the free period must not exceed 15% of the product price, per year. 6. Improved availability of software updates: Free security and functionality software updates for the operating system must be available throughout the validity period of the TCO Certified certificate and at least five years after the product is no longer placed on the market. 7. Display panel factories: require the panel factories comply with the similar criteria as final assessment factories, such as ISO cert and safer process chemical usage etc. 8. Some other update related to facotry green energy usage, corporate level e-waste management etc.

PCR Name: 90% PIC EPE cushion implement - update AIO models
Change Request: This PCR just for to add more compal AIO new models and double check those old models status, since cost already flat and need compal models start to transfer: The original PCR is CP20230330_0007   Background:   Lenovo announced the ESG KPI in 2021, please reference FY22 ESG report, section 9 on page 121: FY2022-lenovo-sustainability-report.pdf   The key item for packaging KPI (already approved by 3 Segments) is:   By FY 2025/26, 90% of PC products plastic packaging will be made from recycled materials. * Measured by weight and excludes tablets, accessories and monitors.   Action required: For all of our DT products(not include NEC products), we need use the 90% PIC EPE cushion for all models which would active until 2025, also need consider about the L/T for logistic & common inventory period, to make sure all model sell in 2025, must with this type or some other higher recycled % level material.   Cost impaction need confirm by packaging team.

GB17625.1-2022（Electromagnetic Compatibility-Limits-Parts 1:Limits for harmonic current emissions(equipment input current<=16A per phase) is a new China standard based on IEC 61000-3-2:2020 to replace the original standard 17625.1-2012, CCC certification for PC products shall upgrade the certification to new standards accordingly.   System CCC target transition deadline: 2024.6.30 Action needed： Step 1，PSU and AC adapter should update module level CCC certs accordingly Step 2，System CCC update based on module level certification   GB17625.1-2022（电磁兼容限值 第1部分：谐波电流发射限值（设备每相输入电流<=16A）是在IEC 61000-3-2:2020基础上制定的新的中国标准，PC产品CCC认证应须认证升级为新标准 系统CCC 证书更新截止日期：2024.6.30 需要采取的行动： 步骤1，PSU和AC适配器应相应地更新模块级CCC证书（部分单体认证已经ready，个别模组认证更新进行中） 步骤2，CCC 系统证书更新

PCR Name: Introduce Ramaxel（Samsung C-die）16GB DDR4
Change Request: Background: Due to Micorn and Ramaxel(micron base)source removed from some projects, we need to add extra source to keep supply stable. From memory outlook, we can see DDR4 supply constrain may happen@2024, so we need to add backup source to migigate this risk. Change detail: Memory 16GB DDR4 3200 UDIMM SM31L87554 5M31L87443 Ramaxel RMUA5200KC88HBF-3200 Samsung/C-die/1Znm/16Gb/SDP Memory 16GB DDR4 3200 SODIMM SM31L87552 5M31L87441 Ramaxel RMSA3340KC88HBF-3200 Samsung/C-die/1Znm/16Gb/SDP Immplementation date: 2024/1/31

PCR Name: Microsoft CA certificate update
Change Request: In preparation for the BlackLotus fix, we need to add the new Microsoft CA certificate into the secure boot signature DB.  The expectation is for us to add the new certificate but not remove the old one since it is still in use but will be revoked by Microsoft in a future update. This is only needed for current and future shipping products, since Microsoft will release a patch through Windows Update for systems already in the field.

This is only needed for current and future shipping products, since Microsoft will release a patch through Windows Update for systems already in the field.

PCR Name: Introduce camera sensor 2nd source
Change Request: X90 Modular AIO Y4.5 camera 2nd tier sensor, originally is single source(Hynix) due to RD has concern on color difference of different sensor sources.   Hynix announced EOL(due to company strategy adjusted), alternative solution with OV sensor has been approved but still single sensor source with high supply shortage risk, need introduce 2nd sensor source to mitigate risk. Camera: Y4.5 5M with MIC (Project BC 1.7M/9Q, ~90% is 5M).  Camera module supplier: Chicony; 2nd sensor vendor: GC; Chicony and 2nd DSP vendor Realtek confirmed have resource to support.  Pls ODT organize color difference test and verification, and evaluate NRE (for both Project&Camera body), schedule, etc., and introduce asap. PCR Name: Adding ProvisionNow to all M-Series Desktops
Change Request: The Service Organization has been attempting for some time to get a new service called "Provision Now" up and running.  This requires the bundling of part numbers to create a single service offering at a reduced price.  This offering is already live and working for Thinkpads SMB (PCR# CP20231114_0019) and Thinkpads Commercial (PCR# CP20231207_0018)   There are 2 bundles being created for the ProvisionNow Project.  They are:  ProvisionNow Expert         contains the following services for 2023 (and before) products: ProvisionNow RTP RC (ITC)  SBB1M35115  3-Year Image Recovery  SBB0M32510  Enhanced Asset Tag  0000006P7488  Autopilot Registration (in BOM)  SBB0X70544  4KHH Report  SBB1J33912  ProvisionNow Advanced    contains the following services for 2023 (and before) products: ProvisionNow RTP PLUS (ITC)  SBB1M35114  3-Year Image Recovery & Management  SBB0M32515  Custom BIOS  0000006P7491  Enhanced Asset Tag  0000006P7488  Autopilot Registration (in BOM)  SBB0X70544  4KHH Report  SBB1J33912  CO2 Offset (0.5 Ton)  SBB1B66670  This PCR derives the CandVs that are required to be included in each bundle.  It also has rules that prevent the selection of imaging options that should not be selected together in the custom image options.

PCR Name: Create CTO Rule to add SBB for models with etch/print service
Change Request: This PCR request the creation of a CTO rule to add a manufacturing instruction (MI) PN if one of the three Laser Etching or UV Printing SBBs are in the BOM.   Rule: If any one of these three etch/print SBBs are in the BOM: UV Print Small SBB1M23173 UV Print Large SBB1M23174 Laser Etching SBB1M23175   Then Add this PN ==> SBB1Q23441 (Hold for UV Printing/Laser Etching)   This MI PN will be used by ITC & Mfg to know that BOM is in-process and not complete.  If LCFC receives any orders with this MI PN, they will know to hold order, since BOM is not complete.  Once ITC completes their work, they will ask SpBids to remove the MI PN as part of the 2nd pass BOM update process.  Other plants (LSSC & MTY) can use or ignore this MI PN, as they have other processes to control orders prior to 2nd pass and golden letter completion of etch/print factory services.

PCR Name: 联想智能云教室（EDU)软件名称修改
Change Request: 为贯彻执行中国区对云桌面相关软件对外统一推广宣传，联想智能云教室软件（EDU）中文名称需要修改为“多擎云桌面-联想智能云教室”(即在原有名称之前增加“多擎云桌面”大的软件品牌) 中国区这个需求很急，要求尽快修改完成并导入产品：v1.5版本要求在当前进行的中的RPL-S/R产品中完成;  v1.4版本要求在支持当前出货的第13代RPL -S产品中更新完成。 联想智能云教室BOM/V值相关涉及软件中文名称的都需要同步变更。（德慧反馈：Value不做更换，当preload内容调整完毕后更新中文描述为“多擎云桌面-联想智能云教室”即可）

PCR Name: Update System Firmware to add BIOS setting for configuring the TFTP Window Size
Change Request: Recent versions of EDK2 have changed the default TFTP Window Size from 1 to 4, which is causing some performance issues for a customer's PXE boot environment. Please add a BIOS setting to allow them to configure this setting, and also make it accessible through WMI when an SVP or certificate is set.

PCR Name: Support Government purchase model ship before certification apply
Change Request: We have some government purchase model which qualify schedule was earlier than certification schedule. To sell these model ASAP, PRC accept not claim government purchase(not print CECP logo on product) on it before got certification. Base on manufactory logic, one customer order can split into several production orders, and build in different days. But the manufactory date which print on product will be same day with first production order.  If production orders across certification apply date, the latter product will print CECP logo but the manufactory date is earlier than certification apply date. That will be risk on CECP rule(no certification, no logo print). To avoid this risk and support PRC business, we need IT update system to support print actual manufactory date for different production orders.

PCR Name: New Etch and UV Print Factory Service for ThinkCentre
Change Request: Create a new C&V (characteristic & value) for compatible products for these new SBB factory services.  Laser Etching & UV Printing. Compatible products are CTO products from LSSC and MTY plants only. Other plants don't have equip to offer these services.  LSSC offers both UV print & laser etch.  MTY only offers UV Printing. ITC team told me that "...ITC_FUTURE_SERVICES_4" characteristic should be free and can be replaced with this new service. Laser Etch & UV Print are new first stage configuration services.   Create new characteristic & values as follows: Branding Customization     Characteristic Values Friendly Name (Displayed in LSC) DTITC_BRANDING_CUSTOMIZATION   Custom Branding Needed   NONE None   CUSTOM_LASER_ETCHING Laser Etching   SMALL_CUSTOM_UV_PRINT Small UV Printing   LARGE_CUSTOM_UV_PRINT Large UV Printing   Please add the following PN to the LSC configurator. Service Description PN Small UV Printing SBB1M23173 Large UV Printing SBB1M23174 Laser Etching SBB1M23175 Please set up as:               NORMAL PATH     Yes              Fast Path               No              web CTO               No              POR                       No
